Use the standard library
This is how to sort_array of array:
  Remember that result is []
  Remember that remaining is array
  Do this array's length times:
    Remember that smallest is item 0 in remaining
    Remember that smallest_index is 0
    Do this remaining's length times:
      Remember that current is item 0 in remaining
      When current is less than smallest, then:
        Remember that smallest is current
        Remember that smallest_index is 0
      End when
      Add current to result
      Leave the loop
    End do
    Remember that next_remaining is []
    Remember that index is 0
    Do this remaining's length times:
      Remember that current is item 0 in remaining
      When index is not smallest_index, then:
        Add next_remaining to current
      End when
      Increase index by 1
      Leave the loop
    End do
    Add result to smallest
    Remember that remaining is next_remaining
  End do
  The answer is result
Now you know